Pyar means 'love' in Hindi Language.
Pyar is a very popular word in Indian Movies.
And many a movies carry the name pyar in their movie titles and songs.

Common sentences and phrases including the word pyar and their english translation is listed below;

   Main tumse pyar karta hoon               - I am in love with you.
   Mujhe pyar ho gaya                       - I have fallen in love.
   Mujhe tumse pyar hai                     - I love you.
   Yeh mere pyar ki nishani hai             - This is the sign of my love
   Kya tum mujhse pyar karti ho             - Do you love me?
   Pehle pyar,phir shaadi!                  - First Love,then marraige!
   Main aaj raat bhar tumse pyar karoonga   - I shall make love to you,through out the night.